targets.query:
from(bucket: "CAN_prod")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "MCB")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "DriveState")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["class"] == "DriverInterface")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")
